commit 96d90a9d517262a9e7e178624c3322af8cba7ce0
Author: Paolo Bacchilega <paobac@src.gnome.org>
Date:	2011-09-10

    Flickr: fixed import of photosets greater then 500

    The method flickr.photosets.getPhotos returns a max of 500 photos,
    call the method multiple times if the photoset contains
    more then 500 photos.

    [bug #648701]

