commit fb2e47efaf11e53429f21f249a07e21fe01dc5b4
Author: Paolo Bacchilega <paobac@src.gnome.org>
Date:	2010-09-17

    fixed crash when changing directoty and a script in generating
    a thumbnail

    do a copy of the job list when cancelling the jobs because the
    the list is modified in the job destructor; in thumbnail_job_cancel
    free the job only if the job didn't start (do not trust
    g_cancellable_is_cancelled because when the thumbnail is
    generated with an external script the cancellable object is not
    used).

M	gthumb/gth-file-list.c

