commit df17e42bddb38955609dd338e3dd84151c9f07b0
Author: Paolo Bacchilega <paobac@src.gnome.org>
Date:	2010-09-02

    Use a two step policy to load images

    In the first step the image is loaded at a smaller size to minimize
    load time, in the second step it is loaded at full size to maximize
    quality.

