commit 140da1c098ed841a4657275089e35b00102912d6
Author: Paolo Bacchilega <paobac@src.gnome.org>
Date:	2010-06-29

    Fix metadata write.

    Save the type in the metadata itself.  Use md->tagLabel() to get
    the description, md->value() to get the raw value and md->print()
    to get the interpreted value.  Use value->read() on the raw value
    to restore the original
    value.

    [bug #623071]

M	extensions/exiv2_tools/exiv2-utils.cpp
M	gthumb/gth-file-data.c
M	gthumb/gth-main.c
M	gthumb/gth-metadata.c
M	gthumb/gth-metadata.h
M	gthumb/gth-pixbuf-list-task.c

