commit ed99b652bed04ef9ba4551f474902211887e36b2
Author: Paolo Bacchilega <paobac@src.gnome.org>
Date:	2010-06-17

    [webalbums] fixed layout issue for fluid indexes

    Always print a non-void value for the thumbnail attribute
    to make the caption of the same height for all the images,
    this fixes a layout issue when the "adapt columns to the
    window width" option is enabled.

