commit 74b88dee8e3cc1d78dc621ba5b2191e506c9bb88
Author: Paolo Bacchilega <paobac@src.gnome.org>
Date:	2010-02-06

    [change_date] implemented adjust timezone

    Implemented the adjust timezone option.
    Removed GTH_CHANGE_EXIF_DATETIME_TAG because it's the same thing
    as comment date, and removed GTH_CHANGE_EXIF_DATETIMEDIGITIZED_TAG
    because it cannot be changed.

