commit ccf9ce891ad638e9817dadd8f8088b4962f04ffe
Author: Paolo Bacchilega <paobac@src.gnome.org>
Date:	2010-01-24

    Revert "Build with gtk > 2.19.3 (GTK_WIDGET_TOPLEVEL ->
    gtk_widget_is_toplevel)"

    This reverts commit a4b16a8bebc644f95179c9b1a391768b7709cd96.

    1) no one can commit without asking to the maintainer.
    2) the patch is not necessary thanks to the previous commit that
       allows to use deprecated API by default.

M	gthumb/eggfileformatchooser.c
M	gthumb/gth-file-tool.c
M	gthumb/gth-tags-entry.c

