commit 8aaebfb74300675996c6b3732bc5d62ff161ee3a
Author: Michael J. Chudobiak <mjc@svn.gnome.org>
Date:	2009-01-23

    Use G_FILE_COPY_TARGET_DEFAULT_PERMS (if glib >= 2.19.0) so that

    2009-01-23	Michael J. Chudobiak  <mjc@svn.gnome.org>

	    * libgthumb/gfile-utils.c: (gfile_xfer):
	    Use G_FILE_COPY_TARGET_DEFAULT_PERMS (if glib >= 2.19.0)
	    so that copied/moved files receive the default permissions
	    for the user (respecting the umask and any directory setgid
	    bits)
	    rather than trying to copy the old permissions.


    svn path=/trunk/; revision=2498

M	ChangeLog
M	libgthumb/gfile-utils.c

