commit b2e455721346aa4591ff2ad021fcca88a2a80aa6
Author: Michael J. Chudobiak <mjc@svn.gnome.org>
Date:	2008-08-15

    Don't put the free space into a gboolean. That's only suitable
    for 1-bit

    2008-08-15	Michael J. Chudobiak  <mjc@svn.gnome.org>

	    * libgthumb/file-utils.c: (get_destination_free_space):
	    Don't put the free space into a gboolean. That's only
	    suitable for
	    1-bit storage systems. guint64 is more capacious.


    svn path=/trunk/; revision=2400

