Date:	2008-02-06

    Removed libiptcdata from gthumb. We use exiv2 instead, now. The
    comment

    2008-02-06	Michael J. Chudobiak  <mjc@svn.gnome.org>

	    * NEWS:
	    * README:
	    * configure.in:
	    * libgthumb/comments.c: (comment_data_new),
	    (comment_data_free),
	    (comment_data_dup), (comment_delete),
	    (load_comment_from_metadata),
