	    (comments_load_comment):
	    * libgthumb/gth-exiv2-utils.cpp:
	    Removed libiptcdata from gthumb. We use exiv2 instead, now.
	    The comment <-> metadata code has been updated to reflect
	    this.
	    The comment <-> metadata mapping is still unstable and
	    may change.


