    2007-04-16	Michael J. Chudobiak  <mjc@cvs.gnome.org>

	    * libgthumb/pixbuf-utils.c: (_gdk_pixbuf_transform):
	    * libgthumb/pixbuf-utils.h:
	    * libgthumb/print-callbacks.c: (print__gdk_pixbuf_rotate):
