    2007-04-09	Michael J. Chudobiak  <mjc@cvs.gnome.org>

	    * libgthumb/gtk-utils.c: (_gtk_request_dialog_run):
	    Return NULL if the dialog text entry is empty, instead of
	    an empty string.


    svn path=/trunk/; revision=1564

